Message.En:
This area near the orc stronghold 
is very dangerous―― 
Haah, what concerns me recently is 
<LQEM>. 
There has been damage to valuable livestock and 
houses―― 
Warrior staying here, please. 
Could you help by eliminating <LQVA> pieces?,
Message.Jp:
オークの砦に近いこの地は危険が多くて――はぁあ
最近気になっているのは<LQEM>なんだ
貴重な家畜や民家への被害もあったし――
逗留中の戦士さん、頼むよ。<LQVA>体退治して助けてくれないかな？
